00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:38.000
biochemist who basically took
whatever it was,

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:42.000
put it in a whirling blender or
something, and ripped everything

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.000
into little pieces.
