00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:42.000
as a hydrogen bond.
The hydrogen bond is about

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:53.000
one-twentieth the strength --

00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:57.000
-- of a covalent bond.
